('Waiting for the Hearse', 'MOVIE', '1985-01-01', NULL, 'comedy', 'Mama Cora, who is almost eighty years old, has three sons and a daughter. She lives with one of them, who has serious financial problems. The family meets one day to celebrate an anniversary meal, and that is when the problem arises: which of them will take care of her?', NULL, '', 8.0, NULL, 'https://www.fss_address.com'),
