('Disco Dancer', 'MOVIE', '1982-01-01', NULL, 'drama, romance', 'Anil, a street singer, is humiliated and driven out of Bombay along with his mother. However, he soon becomes a famous performer but the enemies from his past try to destroy his hard-earned career.', NULL, '', 6.4, NULL, 'https://www.fss_address.com'),
